  "description": "Bank of Hangzhou Co., Ltd. provides various banking products and services in China. The company operates through five segments: Corporate Business, Small Business, Retail Business, Treasury Business, and Other Businesses. It offers deposits, loans, settlements, trade-related products, and other services; and debit cards, credit and mortgage lending, and personal asset management services. The company also provides interbank deposit/lending, repurchase/repurchase agreements, discounting, and investment. It serves individual customers, small businesses, and large and medium-sized enterprise clients. The company was formerly known as Hangzhou City Commercial Bank Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Bank of Hangzhou Co., Ltd. in June 2008. Bank of Hangzhou Co., Ltd. was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Hangzhou, China.",
